Alliance Ethnik is a group of hip-hop french 1990's. It consists of five members from different backgrounds, hence the name Alliance Ethnik (Ethnik being a cacographie the word "ethnic"). 

Alliance Ethnik becomes known in 1995 with the album Standard & Funky which sums up the way the group in the middle of french hip-hop. The album cartonne thanks to singles like Simple & Funky, Respect and Honesty and Jealousy.
